  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Network Engineer",
  "description": "<p>We are representing our client (A Software Engineering Firm) to look for Senior Network Engineer to join their in- house team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive the implementation and compliance of IT policy for network architecture.</li>\n  <li>Assist in security incidents and provide expertise in remediation efforts.</li>\n  <li>Research the latest industry practices and technologies as well as emerging threats and vulnerabilities.</li>\n  <li>Constantly analyze, review and maintain the network baseline required by performing risk and vulnerabilities assessment to ensure the balancing of the resources available and the requirement of sufficient security measures.</li>\n  <li>Manage or participate in new setup or upgrade of network infrastructure projects.</li>\n  <li>Design network structure (including configuring hardware devices)</li>\n  <li>Participate in network related vulnerabilities testing and drill.</li>\n  <li>Participate in IT audit and DRP.</li>\n  <li>Monitor network and system utilization</li>\n  <li>Assist in any other duties as assigned from time to time, where applicable.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/ Diploma in IT/ Computer Science/ Network/ Computing/ Computing Engineering</li>\n  <li>Minimum 4 years of relevant experience in Network infrastructure</li>\n  <li>Familiar with CISCO Systems, Firewall, Router, DNS ,VPN, WAF and IPS etc</li>\n  <li>Service-oriented, interpersonal skills and adaptable to a fast-paced dynamic environment</li>\n  <li>Experience in one or more Cloud platforms such as AWS, Azure, Google, etc for wide range of services</li>\n  <li>Professional certification in CCNA, CCNP and CCIE are advantageous</li>\n  <li>Certifications in Cloud Solutions Architect would be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical and troubleshooting skill.</li>\n  <li>Team player with good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
